Generated map data
==================

CS2FOW `.bvh8` files and matching JSON bake reports are derived from
Counter-Strike 2 game data. They are runtime assets for CS2FOW, but they are not
licensed under the project MIT license.

Each bake is valid only for the map resource CRC and source size recorded in its
JSON report and `.bvh8` header. If Valve updates a map resource, CS2FOW rejects
the old bake and generates or requires a matching replacement.

Distribution of generated map data requires compliance with Valve's applicable
terms.
